"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*o6ggkLXkM_5dZ1BNZ6eSrA.png)\\n\\n## New Feature “Liquidation Reminder” Goes Live\\n\\n**Update：Desktop/Mobile (All Chains)**\\n\\nYou can set the pre-warning values of your \\\\*\\\\*used ratio \\\\*\\\\*and **borrow APY** according to your personal risk tolerance. When the pre-warning value you set is reached, the system will automatically send a notification email to you.\\n\\n## Email Notification Sending Frequency and Rules:\\n\\n**a. For each chain:**Liquidation alert email: Send only one email per day.Borrowing APY alert email: Send only one email per day for each market.\\n\\n**b. For each different chain**The pre-warning values of each chain need to be set separately.The email notifications of each chain are calculated independently.\\n\\n**c. Regarding the confirmation email:**Only 3 confirmation emails are sent a day.After 3 emails, if the pre-warning values or email address are modified on the same day, the modification will still take effect, but no confirmation email will be sent.\\n\\n## How to set？\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Step1: **Click the** \\\\[Liquidation Reminder Settings\\\\] \\\\*\\\\*button on the right side of the **\\\\[My Assets\\\\]** page, or under the \\\\*\\\\*\\\\[Borrow/Repay\\\\] \\\\*\\\\*page\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*R4uufV_-ll3uwYXF.png)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*skOtiELIX4SsBZSp.png)\\n\\n**Step2: Enter the APY pre-warning value to be set and your email address then click** \\\\[Sign and submit\\\\]\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1148/0\\\\*9Pa6x2uzPfR6lK24.png)\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Step3: \\\\[Sign\\\\] \\\\*\\\\*the signature request of MetaMask\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/684/1\\\\*m2Awzx4xgq833hb-iT4MpQ.png)\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Step 4: \\\\*\\\\*After reconfirming the filled information, click **\\\\[Confirm\\\\]** to complete the setting successfully\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/822/0\\\\*JavkTNkfOVs6_vco.png)\\n\\n**Note:**\\n\\n1. This feature is temporarily only available to users who have more than 2000 USD outstanding borrowings.\\n2. When the “used ratio” is too high, you can deposit more collateral assets or repay part of your outstanding borrowings to reduce the risk.\\n3. This function is designed to improve the user experience of WePiggy, does not charge any fees and does not assume any responsibility for the delivery rate.\",\"timestamp\":1636596307,\"title\":\"WePiggy’s New Feature: “Liquidation Reminder” Goes Live\"},\"digest\":\"s-SUxdZr3t5J_1UkaDrJfs1o8W021LDs1ul92FHntrQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"9fM8182SrypuR9jZ_a_xqTh6C5Vh8mhlhGn2neLZhW0lNAWhXrAh4z4CX2wMVHckw9QyNuZf7rnMINbLb2zckQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc82d064579e95fce57e72d8f3e37759f40fd261e5df790f87edb0ce708ab9b09088a8d04cbf29e5ca12f34f0b482a37f2f71c105a2ea08c50f6161ee26251fa01b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"s-SUxdZr3t5J_1UkaDrJfs1o8W021LDs1ul92FHntrQ\"}"